/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: USER */
/*==============================================================*/
create table USER
(
USER_NAME varchar(50) not null,
ROL_NAME varchar(50) not null,
ID_SOLICITUD int,
PASSWORD varchar(50) not null,
ENABLED smallint not null,
NBANNED smallint not null,
LAST_BAN date not null,
primary key (USER_NAME)
);

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: USER_PK */
/*==============================================================*/
create unique index USER_PK on USER
(
USER_NAME
);

);

/*==============================================================*/

(
ID_SOLICITUD
);

alter table USER add constraint FK_USER_ROLES foreign key (ROL_NAME)
references ROLES (ROL_NAME) on delete restrict on update restrict;

alter table USER add constraint FK_USER_SOLICITUD foreign key (ID_SOLICITUD)
references SOLICITUD (ID_SOLICITUD) on delete restrict on update restrict;
